{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d04bd1f5-eb3b-4058-abf5-ea3a047b6f0e", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d04bd1f5-eb3b-4058-abf5-ea3a047b6f0e@1.pkg/1772597532071/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597532327", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d04bd1f5-eb3b-4058-abf5-ea3a047b6f0e@1.pkg/1772597532071/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597532327"}, "identifier": "d04bd1f5-eb3b-4058-abf5-ea3a047b6f0e", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查权利义务相统一</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A:小华的文章被某期刊选用并发表，这体现了小华享有著作权，未涉及义务，故A不符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D:小英的爸爸主动缴纳个人所得税，这是履行依法纳税的义务，未涉及权利，故D不符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C:小美的妈妈被选举为区人大代表，这是享有选举权和被选举权，未涉及义务，故C不符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B:因努力学习获得了&ldquo;三好学生&rdquo;称号，这是履行受教育的义务，享有荣誉权，故B符合题意;故本题选B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）下列生活情境能直接体现&ldquo;权利义务相统一&rdquo;的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）下列生活情境能直接体现“权利义务相统一”的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/qu